In the MATTER OF Jarred S. FREEMAN, an Attorney at Law (Attorney No. 022362009) D-70 September Term 2018
082318 Supreme Court of New Jersey. January 10, 2019

ORDER

This matter having been duly presented, it is ORDERED that Jarred S. Freeman of Edison, who was admitted to the bar of this State in 2009, and who was suspended from the practice of law for a period of three months effective October 8, 2018, by Order of this Court filed September 6, 2018, be restored to the practice of law, effective immediately.
